snippet.description:
Mario Maker Speed Run FAIL! ►► http://bit.ly/1NrjhoU
Subscribing to GLive? A Winning Move! ►►http://bit.ly/1Oo7KH9 

In honor of the awesomeness that is Mario Maker, I play through levels that you guys have created for me: the good, the bad, and the REALLY HARD! Thanks to everyone for submitting your Mario Maker levels and pointing out your favorite episodes to me in the comments for the next episodes!


Follow all the updates on new episodes of GTLive!

Subscribe & hang out with us every day! ►►http://bit.ly/1Oo7KH9
Follow us on Twitter at @MatPatGT and #GTLive

Thanks so much to Thomas Torbergsen for editing the intro for GTLive and a whole bunch of these highlights episodes!
snippet.title: GTLive: Flappy Mario Maker? JUST DO IT! (COMPLETE)
